items.title: Marble Creek Apartments in West Phoenix sell for $16.75 million
items.summary:
The Marble Creek apartments at 5601 W. McDowell Rd. in West Phoenix have been sold to an investor from British Columbia for $16,750,000.  This asset expands the buyer’s portfolio of Greater Phoenix properties to more than 20.  “Marble Creek offered this buyer an extremely well-maintained property with strong occupancy in a great location close toâ€¦ Read More â†’
